text: Sean Paulhus is an American politician from the state of Maine. He is a member of the Maine House of Representatives, representing District 52. He is a member of the Maine Democratic Party. Paulhus served as a city councillor for Bath, Maine. He won a special election to the Maine House of Representatives for the 52nd district on April 2, 2019. ==References== ==External links== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Maine House of Representatives Category:Maine Democrats Category:People from Bath, Maine Category:Maine city council members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
